<view class="page-shell home-page">
  <view class="hero card">
    <view class="hero-title">泉州麻将</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">原生微信小程序 · 本地课分玩法</view>

    <view class="tag-row">
      <text class="pill">144 张</text>
      <text class="pill">庄 17 / 闲 16</text>
      <text class="pill">开金百搭</text>
      <text class="pill">吃碰杠胡</text>
    </view>

    <view class="selector-block">
      <view class="section-title">选择庄底</view>
      <view class="option-row">
        <view
          wx:for="{{bankerBaseOptions}}"
          wx:key="value"
          class="option-chip {{item.value === selectedBankerBase ? 'option-chip-active' : ''}}"
          data-value="{{item.value}}"
          bindtap="selectBankerBase"
        >
          {{item.label}}
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <button class="primary-btn {{starting ? 'page-btn-disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="startGame" disabled="{{starting}}">开始对局</button>
  </view>

  <view class="intro card">
    <view class="section-title">当前已接入</view>
    <view class="intro-item">1. 1 名玩家 + 3 个 AI，本地单机场景</view>
    <view class="intro-item">2. 开局选庄底 10 / 2，按局续分</view>
    <view class="intro-item">3. 计入花牌、金牌、暗刻、碰牌、各类杠和八花</view>
    <view class="intro-item">4. 结果页展示主结算与未胡三家番差</view>
  </view>
</view>
